column4: Молодежное преступление представляет собой любое преступление, совершаемое всеми лицами моложе 18 лет.
Stray animals respersent any animals that have no home or are roaming the streets, whether it's dogs, cats, monkeys or other similar animals.
Orphans and homeless minors are from the age of 0 - 17, they cannot care for themselves or protect themselves.
